replies.bodyText:
You're correct, my mistake. In that case I would suggest to separate the concerns; first you build the list of filters then you build the filter. Something like this:
List<Filter> orFilters = new ArrayList<>();
orFilters.add(lt);
orFilters.add(gt);
if (isNillable(pName)) {
    // the property may have a NULL value, we need to vouch for it
    orFilters.add(pb.getExpression());
}
return ff.or(orFilters);
